On a screen exactly 450px wide, what is the behaviour of the featured cards?

options:
A. 
.container {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  gap: 20px;
}
.featured { grid-column: span 2; }
@media (min-width: 400px) {
  .container { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
}

B. 
.container {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  gap: 20px;
}
@media (max-width: 399px) {
  .container { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}
.featured { grid-column: span 2; }

C. 
.container {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  gap: 20px;
}
@media (min-width: 400px) {
  .container { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  .featured { grid-column: span 2; }
}

D. 
.container {
  display: grid;
  gap: 20px;
}
@media (min-width: 400px) {
  .container { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  .featured { grid-column: span 2; }
}
@media (max-width: 399px) {
  .container { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}

answer:
C. 
.container {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  gap: 20px;
}
@media (min-width: 400px) {
  .container { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  .featured { grid-column: span 2; }
}

